ActDepartment of Employment and Social Development Act
PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 2016-504 of June 14, 2016 by adding the following: As Associate Deputy Minister of Employment and Social Development, LESLIE MacLEAN is, pursuant to paragraph 20(2)(b) of that Act, the Vice-Chairperson of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission. (LESLIE MacLEAN)
